{"tid":1968693,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「連登有愛」希望能夠搵到自閉症手足幫手！！","createTime":"2020-04-11T23:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T08:10:44.000Z","uid":112637,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e08bde6f05ceb4f1b3f5580b2c5931d4ec90a30","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T23:59:51.000Z","msg":"由於武漢肺炎影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且想搵的對象太難揾到<br />\n所以fyp的訪問人數遲遲都未達到目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望連登有愛可以搵到啲手足打救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都知自己衰仔拖到最後一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎仼屌唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係我嘅fyp少少資料<br />\n希望有符合要求的手足可以留低tg<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">或者tg@allpopodienow</span></strong><br />\n大恩大德小弟沒齒難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">基本資料</span></strong><br />\n研究題目：探討自閉症青年的職業傾向如何受到家庭、學校以及社會的影響<br />\n研究對象：集中在15-24歲、患有自閉症的青年<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">（稍微超過呢個range都可以）</span></strong><br />\n研究目的：希望透過了解香港ASD青年的職業傾向，能有利於政府，社會福利機構和社會企業製定更好的策略，通過提供合適的職業生涯服務，尋找與他們的傾向相符的工作，來激勵ASD青年在勞動力市場的長期就業。其最終目的是減少ASD青年的失業率，同時促進社會共融和解決即將到來的社會問題。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">訪問資料</span></strong><br />\n訪問形式：電話訪問<br />\n訪問內容：主要分為三部份，問題數目大約有15題（包括開場的背景問題）。預計訪談時間大約15-30分鐘，視乎於答案的長度。<br />\n訪問日期：比較緊逼，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最好在4月15號前完成（最遲16號），但可以遷就於任何時間都得。</span></strong><br />\n訪問人數：至少需要10人。<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">（目前仲差2個）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">成個訪談過程會被錄音以便後續的分析與整理，但此錄音僅供研究使用，不會有其他用途。另外，其他所有個人資料及私隱亦只供研究使用。</span>"},{"pid":"cbe262c0edeba12e7b773d0a14dc855a4410fe39","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:00:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8d96fa63688c3dd24342019617bad943ad58a4bc","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:00:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b64407b54328bead41933bc9c05228a1b9fcb84c","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:00:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e0391a1c329560e36561ea5917130df829668721","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:00:52.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"3e60209c0f14eaae0bd723e8a3437ffa6afd2da1","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9be7f229f9f876ea756ed336fb1fc894abe211","tid":1968693,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:01:54.000Z","msg":"我朋友嚴重自閉症"},{"pid":"e572d522347245043d06f48da4d89bd724fd0116","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fd4d0f6f1c5ecc348ee1cecdc521274aebcabd","tid":1968693,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":