":"搵咗啲實習社企的老細但合資格又肯interview的唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261430851b8bd30249dcaa2b2d4b2a89bda826d5","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed29076da77f27e16c63e0c54b9e50d29a0acb3a","tid":1968693,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1892ee42fc6a0ac0d576a9908de60d863d6b9d0","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29fd4d0f6f1c5ecc348ee1cecdc521274aebcabd","tid":1968693,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:18:32.000Z","msg":"twitch 大撚把"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:23:57.000Z","msg":"真係有定講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係唔係咁清楚twitch"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:28:23.000Z","msg":"男嘅autism 女嘅賣肉<br />\n唔係鬼人有睇你咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T06:52:09.000Z","msg":"明白曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可惜我唔熟"},{"pid":"9959e23632c9512ab172e0694cbafd4deb5b0658","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"834eeec4a287e7e322bb06599304124756064b52","tid":1968693,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:02:49.000Z","msg":"點先算ASD (撘單問埋ADHD)<br />\na psychotherapist says I have<br />\na psychiatrist says I don't<br />\nadditional info: once had clinically diagnosed depression and OCD"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"其實我都係搵資料睇返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比唔到真係專業嘅答案 不過普遍都有社交障礙 一啲特定同重複嘅習慣<br />\n呢啲特徴其實上網睇都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我又同過ASD的同事相處過 亦都有一個ADHD的best friend 可能個人經驗上都覺得有唔同<br />\n例如話社交上ADHD係主動啲 同埋佢哋言語上表達好直接 思維比較跳躍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但ASD佢哋言語上/說話能力上可能會有啲小問題好似詞不達意咁 同埋通常被動啲<br />\n但佢哋共同點都係有時get唔到所謂嘅潛規則 （社交禮議？）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5f1989eb9c49b46a229bbff1224272646d2faa","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9959e23632c9512ab172e0694cbafd4deb5b0658","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"834eeec4a287e7e322bb06599304124756064b52","tid":1968693,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:02:49.000Z","msg":"點先算ASD (撘單問埋ADHD)<br />\na psychotherapist says I have<br />\na psychiatrist says I don't<br />\nadditional info: once had clinically diagnosed depression and OCD"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"其實我都係搵資料睇返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比唔到真係專業嘅答案 不過普遍都有社交障礙 一啲特定同重複嘅習慣<br />\n呢啲特徴其實上網睇都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我又同過ASD的同事相處過 亦都有一個ADHD的best friend 可能個人經驗上都覺得有唔同<br />\n例如話社交上ADHD係主動啲 同埋佢哋言語上表達好直接 思維比較跳躍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但ASD佢哋言語上/說話能力上可能會有啲小問題好似詞不達意咁 同埋通常被動啲<br />\n但佢哋共同點都係有時get唔到所謂嘅潛規則 （社交禮議？）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:04:08.000Z","msg":"社交<span style=\"color: red;\">禮儀</span>"},{"pid":"f763df156ee53742e826f2fb52f55fe59366b839","tid":1968693,"uid":313643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9959e23632c9512ab172e0694cbafd4deb5b0658","tid":1968693,"uid":112637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"834eeec4a287e7e322bb06599304124756064b52","tid":1968693,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:02:49.000Z","msg":"點先算ASD (撘單問埋ADHD)<br />\na psychotherapist says I have<br />\na psychiatrist says I don't<br />\nadditional info: once had clinically diagnosed depression and OCD"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"其實我都係搵資料睇返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比